{
  "stem": "12674.3",
  "chunk_idx": 1,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 3.3,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I used to have a-- a bag, like a sort of a-- a zipper case, which I used to wear.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And I-- I used to make myself a star with little hooks on it, the pins that I bent in the-- in the six corners.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And I used to pin it on me when I went out, and I used to wear the bag.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And-- and when I went out-- and as soon as I came out the door, so my father wouldn't see that I took it off, because he wouldn't have let me-- nobody would have let me walk out of the house-- I would take it off underneath the bag and put it into my pocket.",
      "word_count": 55
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I don't know how many times I scratched my hands on the pin corner.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And on the way back, I would take it and put it on and then wear with this thing on with my handbag under my arm and go home and-- and coming there.",
      "word_count": 33
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "In all the years ever, I didn't wear it until I came to Theresienstadt.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "I wasn't-- they considered it a mark of shame.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And I was going-- I was not going to wear a mark of shame, and nobody was going to make me.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "I wasn't going to walk around in the street.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "They were-- the people would spit at you and things like that.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And I wasn't going to let this happen, and I didn't.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "It was not one-- it's not one of the proudest moments in my life, but I was lucky.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "I didn't do it.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "[LAUGHS] Well, when I was-- in the year 1940, when I was 14 years old, I-- they wanted to have agricultural workers for-- well, they-- they-- they took Jews.",
      "word_count": 29
    }
  ],
